videos.description: Austin Reaves hits three consecutive 3-pointers, and then he gets a dunk in transition.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Reaves is on fire

videos.description: Shizz Alston Jr. tips the inbounds pass then takes it all the way for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Alston Jr.'s hustle leads to dunk for Temple

videos.description: Shizz Alston Jr. makes a nice pass to Nate Pierre-Louis cutting and he throws down a nasty one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Temple's Pierre-Louis gets angry with the rim

videos.description: Quinton Rose jumps in the passing lane and takes it all the way for a vicious one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Owls' Rose feisty defense leads to dunk

videos.description: Shizz Alston Jr. drives and double-clutches for the game-tying layup.
videos.headline: Owls' Alston Jr.  ties the game with clutch bucket

videos.description: Shockers' Markis McDuffie misses a wide-open 3-pointer as time expires.
videos.headline: Temple escapes after McDuffie's missed 3-pointer
